<br>
I recently got myself a Frostbringer.  I am pretty much broke after getting it so will be some time before any further weapon upgrades.  My only real choice for other weapon is one of my bloodpoints.  My question is, which is the suggested configuration?  Frosty/BP or BP/Frosty.  I played some last night in the Hole with Frosty/BP and that seemed to work best?  I usually am grouped with a 53 Enchanter so I have good haste and am in werewolf form.<br>
<br>
Also, I asked this in another thread but ill ask it here since it is related.  What weapon should I be shooting for to go with the Frosty?.  I should be able to get 10k or relatively soon.  What about the Shimatar of Emerald Dawn?<br>
<br>
