<br>
I have Black Acrylia Halbard as my 2h.  Not as good as the Axe you all mention but I will try using that when duoing next time.<br>
<br>
My guild has already gotten the General Sword for one of our higer level warriors.  Ill see if i can organize getting me one!!<br>
